ext_bw":"A^abit~apN","text_ar":"اَبِتَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) A verse of Tarafeh cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAEa","text_ar":"بَاعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"exhibits an ex. of the former signification. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utensils and furniture of the house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"household goods:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) pl. as above. (K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuw^oxa*u minokumo Eu$oru AlbataAti","text_ar":"لَا يُوْخَذُ مِنْكُمْ عُشْرُ البَتَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tithe of the utensils"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the house or tent shall not be taken from you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) i. e., no poor-rate shall be levied upon such utensils &c. that are not for traffic. (A 'Obeyd.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","K"]},{"entry_id":"n1698","headword_ar":"بَتَّاتٌ","root":"bt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bat~iY~N","text_ar":"بَتِّىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A maker,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seller, of the kind of garment called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bat~","text_ar":"بَتّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K"]}]}}